></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 96<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(4/8/02 3:50:10 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub77.ezboard.com/ftallonzektimes4735guildsoftallonzek.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=562.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ALL LIGHT GUILDS READ!!!</span><hr size=1> /roleplay<br>lolyen anyone who groups with or assists darks or has them in their guild is/are traitors to the light races who advocate goodness over evil.  You will alwyas be eeevvviiil, get over it.  I will try to kill all of you.<br>Traitors must die.<br>/roleplay off<br>I play this game good vs evil lite versus dark.  If that mean I have talls and shorts in my guild or my group, so what it is against a greater evil, the darkness that is trying to overwhelm the side of holy right.  So there is a difference.  If I wanted to group with darks I would have gone to a blue server. <p>"Character is what you are in the dark" and when no one is looking!<BR>Archaic Arbitrator's Leader with an eye on Justice and the Family of Archaic Arbitrators.</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#00000F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub77.ezboard.com/btallonzektimes4735.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=terrimoth>Terrimoth</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(4/8/02 4:32:18 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub77.ezboard.com/ftallonzektimes4735guildsoftallonzek.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=562.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ALL LIGHT GUILDS READ!!!</span><hr size=1> That's a very hazy line there, Toldek.  Does AA have any gnome sk's or necros?  How about any Wizards that follow Solosek Ro?  Human necro's or SK's?<br><br>Tallon Zek is made for teams, so the roleplay aspect would have to be a little askewed to keep up with that premise.  It would mean that an elf, who could attack a gnome, would because for some reason he doesn't like that gnome.  You wanted to play for the roleplay purposes of good vs evil, no offense or anything, but you should play Sullen.<br><br>Besides, he said x-teaming.  You either x-team or you don't, and the majority of the server does, even if they don't want to admit it. I, personally, play dark only.<br><br>Kraglor<br>19 Shadowknight<br><br>Terrimoth<br>16 Necromancer <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000028><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub77.ezboard.com/ulunanare.showPublicProfile?language=EN>lunanare</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Amazonians Slave Keeper</span><br>  Posts: 390<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(4/8/02 5:43:54 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub77.ezboard.com/ftallonzektimes4735guildsoftallonzek.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=562.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://ew2.lysator.liu.se/loth/c/l/claire/syrela.jpg height=200 width=145></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ALL LIGHT GUILDS READ!!!</span><hr size=1> (This message was left blank) <p>"Do not ask which creature screams in the night, Do not question who waits for you in the shadow. It is my cry that wakes you in the night, And my body that crouches in the shadow. I am Lunanare and you are the puppet That dances to my tune." </p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub77.ezboard.com/ulunanare.showPublicProfile?language=EN>lunanare</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0> at: 4/8/02 5:45:31 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#00000F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub77.ezboard.com/uslintyrwolfbane.showPublicProfile?language=EN>slintyr wolfbane</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle